This paper presents a control algorithm for mobile robots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The algorithm is based on probabilistic belief, which suggests the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The paper also mentions the use of hierarchical controllers and MDPs, which are related to control systems (cs.SY) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
